cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO 

This paper involves the use of reinforcement learning and natural language processing to reason about spatial environments, which suggests it could fall under several sub-categories. Specifically, cs.AI seems likely given the use of RL, as does cs.CL given the focus on language understanding. Additionally, the use of representation learning could place this paper in cs.LG or cs.CV, while the simulated environment and agent-based approach could suggest cs.RO.
